<section class="oe_container">
   <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
           <h2 class="oe_slogan" style="color:olive;">Account Budget Alert / Warning</h2>
           <h3 class="oe_slogan" style="color:green;">Only for Odoo Community Edition.</h3>
           <p class="oe_mt32" style="color:olive;">
            This app allow you to raise warnings and alert for budget exceed situations on Sales Order, Invoices and Purchase Orders. <br/>
           </p>
           <p style="color:CRIMSON;">
                <b>Main Features:</b>
           </p>
           <p style="color:olive;">
                <ul style="color:olive;">
                    <li style="color:olive;">Account Invoice
                        <ul>
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Stop / Restrict, popup alert generate for sheduled budget and stop validate process of Account Invoice.</li> 
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Warn Message, only popup message generate for sheduled budget.</li>
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Ignore, In this case no alert generate for sheduled budget.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li style="color:olive;">Vendor Bill
                        <ul>
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Stop / Restrict, popup alert generate for sheduled budget and stop validate process of Vendor Bill.</li> 
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Warn Message, only popup message generate for sheduled budget.</li>
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Ignore, In this case no alert generate for sheduled budget.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li style="color:olive;">Sale Order
                        <ul>
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Stop / Restrict, popup alert generate for sheduled budget and stop confirm process of Sale Order.</li> 
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Warn Message, only popup message generate for sheduled budget.</li>
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Ignore, In this case no alert generate for sheduled budget.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li style="color:olive;">Purchase Order
                        <ul>
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Stop / Restrict, popup alert generate for sheduled budget and stop confirm order process of Purchase.</li> 
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Warn Message, only popup message generate for sheduled budget.</li>
                            <li style="color:olive;">When alert type is Ignore, In this case no alert generate for sheduled budget.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li style="color:olive;">For more details please see video and below screenshots.</li>
                    <li style="color:red;">This module is compitible only for Odoo Community Edition.</li>
<!--                    <li style="color:olive;">When forcefully needed customer signature, your signature is required to process payment.</li>-->
<!--                    <li style="color:olive;">For more details please watch video and screenshots..</li>-->
                </ul>
           </p>
   </div>
</section>

